snippet.title: Fighting Men of Rhodesia ep66 | Maj. Nigel Henson 3rd Talk | Trial & Tribulation
snippet.description:
Part 3. This talented Fire Force commander probably experienced more call-outs than anyone else as the OC of Support Commando, RLI. His military career spanned most of the Rhodesian Bush War from 1965-1980. In this series of talks, Nigel shares some of the highlights of those unforgettable times. When a nation was fighting for survival against overwhelming odds.
